          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The photoproton knockout reaction on 16O leaving 15N",
                " in low-lying bound states has been observed over the",
                " photon energy range from 196 to 361 MeV. The angular",
                " distributions for the reaction populating the ground",
                " state of 15N develops sharp structure as photon",
                " energy is increased but that for population of the",
                " excited states is smooth. The results are not",
                " explained by existing theoretical models."
              ]
            }
          ],
